    "Replaces Root storage with Server storage on the Overview page.",
    "Hides external host filesystem totals when the server capacity cannot be measured reliably.",
    "Shows locally measured server usage and supports an explicit WFILEMANAGER_STORAGE_CAPACITY_BYTES limit.",
    "Routes system telemetry through a server-scoped runtime and uses cgroup-aware memory limits.",
    "Clarifies that managed Supabase is intended for fast setup and testing with a 100 MB data limit per server.",
    "Recommends local SQLite and a dedicated domain for durable long-term installations."
